  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Admins can configure which information fields are required when creating or editing a Customer Profile. At a minimum, RepairQ requires a First Name, Last Name, and Primary Phone number to create a profile. Fields marked as required cannot be bypassed when creating a new customer, and any new requirements will also apply when editing existing customer profiles. This ensures that essential customer information is consistently captured, improving data accuracy and compliance with business needs.</p><p>Customer Required Fields are available to users on RepairQ Advanced and RepairQ Professional plans.</p><h3 id=\"RequiredFieldsforCustomerProfiles-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933344786/Creating+a+Customer+Profile\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933344786\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Create a Customer Profile</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933312070/Managing+Customer+Profiles\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933312070\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Managing Customer Profiles</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/2036891839/Zip+Code+Validation+for+Customers\" data-linked-resource-id=\"2036891839\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Zip Code Validation for Customers</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933869089/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"RequiredFieldsforCustomerProfiles-UpdatingRequiredFieldsforCreatingNewCustomers\">Updating Required Fields for Creating New Customers</h2><p /><p>From the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Settings \u2192 Company Settings</strong>. On the Settings Overview page, under the Customers section, select <strong>Required Fields</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" alt=\"Validation 1.png\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933869089/Validation%201.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" alt=\"Validation 2.png\" width=\"539\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933869089/Validation%202.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>On the Validation Rule Settings screen, you can select additional required fields when adding a new customer. By default, RepairQ requires unique entries for <strong>First Name</strong>, <strong>Last Name</strong>, and <strong>Primary Phone Number</strong>. In the image below, the user has added <strong>Email</strong> and <strong>Zip Code</strong> to the list of required fields. Once you're satisfied with your selections, click <strong>Save</strong> to apply the changes.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" alt=\"Validation 4.png\" width=\"380\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933869089/Validation%204.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"RequiredFieldsforCustomerProfiles-RequiredFieldswhenCreatingaProfile\">Required Fields when Creating a Profile</h2><p>When creating a customer, additional required fields will be marked with an asterisk (*) next to the field. The tab for any sub-category where additional required fields are located will also display an asterisk. For better visibility, required fields will appear on the <strong>General</strong> tab during the customer creation process.</p><p><strong>Note</strong>: If you add a new required field, it will apply to new customers and when editing existing customer profiles. Additionally, if <strong>Zip Code Validation</strong> is enabled, the <strong>Zip Code</strong> field must be filled out for all customers.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"633\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933869089/Validation%206.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.20.X</p>",
